KRUSKAL(G)
    // G = Graph with vertices V and edges E

    MST ← empty set

    sort all edges of G in increasing order of weight

    for each vertex v in G:
        MAKE-SET(v)     // create separate sets

    for each edge (u, v) in sorted edges:
        if FIND-SET(u) ≠ FIND-SET(v):
            add edge (u, v) to MST
            UNION(u, v)

    return MST
